        <mxCell id="s5_ctc_info" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:8px;color:#555&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;CTC Details:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Blank token: 0&lt;br&gt;• Alphabet: 37 (0-9 + A-Z + blank)&lt;br&gt;• Loss: CTC (zero_infinity=True)&lt;br&gt;• Decode: Greedy argmax&lt;br&gt;• Removes repeats &amp;amp; blanks&lt;br&gt;• Handles variable-length output&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
